        <p class="mg-kicker mg-install-kicker">Magpie · not reachable</p>
        <h2 class="mg-install-title">
          Bring this page to life by running Magpie on your Mac.
        </h2>
        <p class="mg-install-dek">
          This is the hosted window into a clipboard app that lives on your
          own machine. Nothing leaves the device unless you press <em>push</em>.
          Set-up takes about sixty seconds.
        </p>
        <ol class="mg-install-steps">
          <li>
            <span class="mg-step-n">1</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Download the latest build.</strong>
              <a href="https://github.com/Good-Feels/magpie/releases/latest" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                github.com/Good-Feels/magpie/releases
              </a>
              — drag <code>Magpie.app</code> to Applications.
