              at <code>pointcast.xyz/api/ping</code>, so this is usually
              zero work — but if you're running a fork or a local broadcast,
              set the endpoint under <em>Preferences → PointCast → Connection</em>.
              Use the <em>Test Connection</em> button to confirm; Magpie
              persists the endpoint + your <em>From</em> name + optional
              Tezos address and the hosted UI reads them from the peer-node's
              <code>/config.json</code>.
              <div class="mg-endpoint-copy">
