            <li><span class="mg-dest-code">BC</span><span class="mg-dest-name">bitchat</span><span class="mg-dest-note">Nostr + BLE mesh · 280</span></li>
            <li><span class="mg-dest-code">BS</span><span class="mg-dest-name">Bluesky</span><span class="mg-dest-note">AT Proto · 300 · rich cards</span></li>
            <li><span class="mg-dest-code">TW</span><span class="mg-dest-name">Twitter / X</span><span class="mg-dest-note">OAuth 2.0 · 280 · threads</span></li>
            <li><span class="mg-dest-code">LI</span><span class="mg-dest-name">LinkedIn</span><span class="mg-dest-note">UGC posts · 3000</span></li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mg-kicker mg-destinations-subkicker">shipping next · v1.0 · skeletons in place, real paths activate with crypto deps</p>
          <ul class="mg-destinations-grid">
            <li class="mg-dest-future"><span class="mg-dest-code">IG</span><span class="mg-dest-name">Instagram</span><span class="mg-dest-note">Graph API · Business account</span></li>
            <li class="mg-dest-future"><span class="mg-dest-code">ZO</span><span class="mg-dest-name">Zora</span><span class="mg-dest-note">MINT on Base · EVMSigner</span></li>
            <li class="mg-dest-future"><span class="mg-dest-code">OB</span><span class="mg-dest-name">Objkt</span><span class="mg-dest-note">MINT on Tezos · Teia FA2</span></li>
            <li class="mg-dest-future"><span class="mg-dest-code">OS</span><span class="mg-dest-name">OpenSea</span><span class="mg-dest-note">Seaport listings · post-mint reach</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="mg-install-cta">
          <a class="mg-btn primary" href="https://github.com/Good-Feels/magpie/releases/latest" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Download · macOS 13+</a>
          <a class="mg-btn ghost" href="https://github.com/Good-Feels/magpie" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a>
